About WATERFRONT
Crafting Delights,
Creating Memories
It’s a true indulgence. Weaving a cosmopolitan flair through our laid-back ambiance, our menu takes influence from the best of culinary excellence. Imagine a dash of Miami exoticism, a pinch of beachy allure, and a splash of Stuart charm, coming together to carve an unparalleled dining destination. It’s a space where pops of sophistication lie around every corner, balancing exquisite seafood and a crowd-pleasing cocktail list with the ultimate boho setting.
Unmatched Culinary Experience
.
Exceptional Customer Service
